set_network_terminal_type

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_network_terminal_type -  This method handles the responses from the remote site informing us of their terminal type.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int set_network_terminal_type(string name)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^name%^RESET%^ - the terminal type gathered from the remote site
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
0 if the type was not used, 1 if it was
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/global/player/events.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method handles the responses from the remote site informing
us of their terminal type.
